Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:09.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥 我要給她換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:12.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:26.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才愛理打來了電話 說是和前輩家裡聯繫了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:29.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.77,0:00:35.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃可以去睡了 接下來由我看著就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:36.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:46.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:48.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:07.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩 你一個人太過努力了

Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:49.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡是?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:57.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊 我…

Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:09.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\pos(1095,580)}{\pos(980,560)}{\3c&HB58E00&}{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs40\fad(500,300)}相同顏色的兩人

Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:05.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:12.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:15.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:18.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還想多看看你的睡臉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:19.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:24.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}身體怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:27.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 好很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:29.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:34.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:35.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:43.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 我去給你倒杯水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:46.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:15.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:22.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那今天就在家裡好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:25.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}動物就交給我們好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:29.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 但要發生了什麼就聯繫我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:36.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個是前輩的手機號碼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:37.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.89,0:04:38.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:42.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但今天就交給我們 你好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:44.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}身體最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:46.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好…的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:50.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天沒能聯繫你 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:53.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不知道紗凪的手機號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我怎麼可能告訴你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:05:00.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 怎麼會把前輩交給你這樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:02.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}得後悔一輩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:06.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 真想早點見到美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:09.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天讓她回去休息了 你沒辦法見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:10.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:19.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 美羽 吃午飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:20.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊

Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:22.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:26.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 前輩 為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:32.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 不管怎樣都很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:33.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我馬上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:44.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你真是的

Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:57.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是個很好的人 你們覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:05:59.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:00.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:02.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:07.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要養的話只養雌性的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:14.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那這樣的話 新吾和美羽怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:19.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}必須要分離才行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:25.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:26.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:39.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會有人好好疼愛你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:45.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}老師 這孩子就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:49.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:57.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也得回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:03.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 回去就好好睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:23.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別哭了 美羽已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:29.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託你 不要再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:31.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}寂寞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:35.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來一直都是在一起的 肯定會寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:39.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們回去以後 它又只剩下一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:43.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}最好能早點找到新吾的飼主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:46.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔多去問問看別人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:48.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們也去問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:52.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我來養
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:53.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在說什麼 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:56.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想養
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:57.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:02.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這麼說起來 前一段時間美羽前輩說不能養是因為?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:05.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係的 又不是什麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:06.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:07.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:11.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我說養就養了 就沒人贊成我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:16.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔認為 要是小紗凪的話很讓人值得放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:18.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 安心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:22.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 我是沒有反對的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:24.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是… 真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這和你沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.89,0:08:28.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:32.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪要是說可以的話 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:33.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}全員一致同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:37.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那今天開始我們就好好相處吧 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:55.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 今天晚上一起睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:57.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也一起洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:02.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾的話 我的全部都可以讓你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:04.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 新吾好H啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼聽起來像我很壞一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:10.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:14.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我又不是對你說 是對新吾說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:16.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:20.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}需要準備的東西好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:23.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}洗手間套裝 食物還有裝水的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:27.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}修甲器 還需要玩具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:31.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你真的是很喜歡新吾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:32.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過事先說明 我喜歡的可不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:37.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:38.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:43.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:49.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果沒事的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:53.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}稍微等下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:55.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:56.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:59.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你好 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:06.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}交換號碼了 你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:10.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道了 那明天午飯後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:13.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:18.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說是想對昨天的事情道謝 招呼我去她家做客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:20.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:26.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}覺得有些緊張 該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:30.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你可別想些不知廉恥的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:32.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才不會想那些事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:35.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是對美羽前輩做什麼奇怪的事 我一定會殺了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:37.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都說不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:40.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天她家人好像也在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}該說是不會做呢 還是做不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 說起來就是不會去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:45.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:50.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 紗凪去過前輩家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:51.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:55.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她家人是什麼樣的人 有兄弟姐妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別拘束 放鬆就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:26.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 美羽前輩身體怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:29.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 完全好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:35.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時候對新吾說了 真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:37.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:41.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 我現在在烤餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:43.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那之前 你先和孩子們玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:48.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:50.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:52.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:03.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:10.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前幾天幫了美羽 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:13.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 不會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:16.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一直從美羽那裡聽說新吾的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:21.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說有個比她年紀小的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:26.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是願意的話 下回和我一起過夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:27.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:28.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:33.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不… 好漂亮的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:37.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真不愧是美羽前輩的姐…姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:40.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她可以 我就不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:43.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的 請冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:51.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 就是想確認幫助美羽的是什麼樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:53.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:58.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是新吾的話 看起來可以放心拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:01.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 拜託什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:10.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽是個喜歡逞強 什麼都攬在自己身上的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:16.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 那個我也有感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:25.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個孩子 小時候養的貓死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:28.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這就成了她心中的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:32.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感情太深了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:37.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}連自然終老的動物 都覺得自己負有責任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:45.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 能在她身邊支持著她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:56.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白了 我會盡可能待在前輩身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:09.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那… 我和新吾什麼時候結婚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:10.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:14.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等等 你在做什麼呢 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:16.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:25.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還以為是姐姐呢 原來是母親啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:27.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:28.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 不會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很好的母親呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:33.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 你喜歡人妻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:35.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:37.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:38.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:41.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:42.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:44.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:47.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}烤得好 烤得很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:48.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你為什麼在這
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}試毒啊 試毒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:52.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才沒有放毒藥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:56.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那可不行 那麼可怕的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:57.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:15:00.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那新吾 就慢慢來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:05.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要好好相處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:07.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:13.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的是對不起了 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:17.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能看到和平時不一樣的前輩 我很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:20.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:32.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾真的好容易讓動物親近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:35.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:39.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小熊喵對新吾不也很親近嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:43.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我沒有養過貓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:48.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但覺得美羽新吾和這些孩子都很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:50.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:54.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能加入喵咪部 真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:55.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:58.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和美羽前輩關係也變好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:05.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也很高興能和新吾關係變得親近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:19.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天真的是很謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:21.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還拿了禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:25.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 該道謝的是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:29.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}下回櫻乃也能一起來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 我會轉告她的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:37.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那… 社團再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:39.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:48.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給櫻乃打個電話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:55.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:57.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}手機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:16:59.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:01.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:08.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}媽媽 幫我抓住加林和托莫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:10.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:13.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊新吾 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:20.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:25.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:30.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天要怎麼面對前輩才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:35.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請不要太在意 像平常那樣對待就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:46.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 如果這樣就道別 可能會這麼一直尷尬下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:51.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再一次送你到公園可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的很多事 太對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:00.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼前輩要道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個… 沒想到會有那樣的事情發生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:06.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我什麼都沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:10.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還不如說看到的好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:15.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我看到了 全部都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:16.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:20.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到底怎麼說才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:22.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:23.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:26.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天開始也好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:28.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:30.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:33.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但有件事我想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:35.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:40.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無論什麼事都不要逞強 要和我商量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:43.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難得在一個社團裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:46.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}希望你也能依賴我一些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:50.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我答應你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:06.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:08.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好

Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:17.00,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和貓生活手冊

Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:17.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩她家怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.89,0:19:18.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:21.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒做什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:22.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}當然沒做了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:25.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理應如此了 別說得好像自己很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:28.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的是的 對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:32.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過 我和新吾可是非常恩愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:33.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:40.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 拍得真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:45.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想要這張照片嗎 特別地我可以送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:48.86,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,500)\pos(640,534)}若想獲得紗凪的待機圖片 請在節目結束之後登陸本動畫官網♪ 免費向智能手機開放下載
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:46.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:48.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:55.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…

Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:19:59.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:01.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:05.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}腹部長肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:09.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算不這麼做 已經很瘦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.44,0:20:12.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 好像自己看過的語氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:12.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:16.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒看到 什麼都沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒錯 新吾沒有做錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:25.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:27.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 小紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:31.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聽新吾說你收養了那隻小貓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}擅自就決定了 真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:37.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會 只要小紗凪沒關係那就沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:42.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後 多餘的玩具如果需要就拿去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:51.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給你 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:54.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:56.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:07.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小紗凪 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:10.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:16.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:23.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:26.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.73,0:21:28.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:35.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 這是怎麼回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:37.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}發生什麼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.53,0:21:39.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:43.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:49.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.97,0:21:52.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:31.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔就算是涼水也沒關係的 主人
